ure capital and founded mason cabot  investment bank he founded liquidxscom inc he founded eworks inc and served as its partner since  he was a principal of mason cabot llc from november  to december  he served at stires and odonnell inc mr bordes served as the chief executive officer of arc communications inc from july  to april  he was the founder of empire media inc and served as its chairman and cochief executive officer he served as chairman of arc communications inc he served as chairman and director of roomlinx from june   to july   he serves as a director of peekyou llc he serves on the boards of or is an advisor to a number of traditional new media and technology companies such as movi mode  northstar software and wwwjiwirecom he serves as a trustee at lee bordes revocable trust peter a bordes jr  gift trust peter a bordes marital trust and bftw llc he has been a director of nbg radio network inc since october   and beasley broadcast group inc since november   he served as a member of advisory board of oncard marketing inc citypulse ltd and roomlinx inc he served as a director of arc communications inc from september  to june   dialog group inc since august   and elgin technologies inc since july  mr bordes served as a director of liquidxscom incread full background corporate headquarters  west th streetnew york new york united statesphone fax  board members memberships directorliquidxscom incdirectorpeekyou llcpresentdirectornbg radio network incpresentdirectorbeasley broadcast group inc education there is no education data available other affiliations beasley broadcast group incliquidxscom incarc communications incnbg radio network incdialog group incgreater media incempire media incelgin technologies incroomlinx inc prior to reverse merger with signal point holdings corpadvaliant incmediatrust inconcard marketing incpeekyou llccitypulse ltd annual compensation there is no annual compensation data available stocks options there is no stock options data av